==Post-event==
===Talking to the Easter Bunny===
* '''Easter Bunny:''' Thank you again for finding Archibald, [player name]!
* '''Player:''' You're very welcome.
* {{tselect|Select an option}}
* {{topt|What are you going to do now?}}
** '''Player:''' What are you going to do now?
** '''Easter Bunny:''' My eggs and I are going to spread the Easter cheer to the fine city of Varrock.
** '''Easter Bunny:''' Many people grow up without chocolate, you know. It's just not right.
** '''Player:''' So true. What has the world come to?
** {{Tact|other}}
* {{topt|Why did you decide to celebrate Easter in Varrock?}}
** '''Player:''' Why did you decide to celebrate Easter in Varrock?
** '''Easter Bunny:''' All of Gielinor deserve to celebrate Easter. I figured Varrock is a particularly busy place.
** '''Easter Bunny:''' By positioning myself here I maximise my CTPOTR.
** '''Player:''' C.. T.. what?
** '''Easter Bunny:''' CTPOTR. Chocolate to person over time ratio. You need to maximise your reach and minimise time spent, to optimise value.
** '''Player:''' I see. I never realised how seriously you took this.
** '''Easter Bunny:''' Of course. Easter only happens once a year. I have to make the most out of it.
** {{Tact|other}}
* {{topt|Can you tell me more about the Easter eggs?}}
** '''Player:''' Can you tell me more about the Easter eggs?
** '''Easter Bunny:''' The eggs are a family tradition. Hatching them, caring for them, watching them develop. This is the job of an Easter Bunny.
** '''Player:''' Hold on. Are you saying there are more Easter bunnies?
** '''Easter Bunny:''' Oh yes, my mother was one. And my father. And their parents before them.
** '''Easter Bunny:''' Maybe one day you can become one too!
** '''Player:''' I'm more of an adventurer-type person, myself.
** {{Tact|other}}

